children.name: Effects
children.text:
You feel unshackled. You gain the following movement benefits while this spell is in effect:
- Your movement is unaffected by difficult terrain
- You can't be magically restrained or paralyzed
- Your speed can't  be magically reduced
- If you're in a grapple or nonmagically restrained, you can use 5 feet of movement to escape
- You can move and attack normally while underwater
